    public class RpcService
extends de.dhbw.ravensburg.verteiltesysteme.de.dhbw.ravensburg.verteiltesysteme.rpc.SamplingMessageGrpc.SamplingMessageImplBase
    This class implements remote procedure calls specified the service.proto file by extending the automatically generated gRPC SamplingMessageGrpc.SamplingMessageImplBase This implementation is getting deployed to a gRPC server instance to expose the specified remote procedure calls.
